@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Pilot" as Pilot
participant ":System" as System

activate Pilot

Pilot -> System : Requests to add weather data to a flight plan

activate System
System --> Pilot : Requests flight plan and weather data
deactivate System

Pilot -> System : Provides flight plan and weather data

activate System
System --> System : Check if pilot is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate flight plan
System --> System : Check if flight plan belongs to pilot
System --> System : Validate weather data
System --> System : Check if flight plan was previously tested

alt flight plan and weather data are valid
    System --> System : Add weather data to flight plan

    alt flight plan was previously tested
        System --> System : Mark previous test result as void
        System --> System : Mark flight plan as requiring new test
    else flight plan was not previously tested
        System --> System : Keep flight plan as not yet tested
    end

    System --> Pilot : Weather data added successfully
else flight plan or weather data is invalid
    System --> Pilot : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate Pilot

@enduml